陳禮潭、李明煌、洪國軒，2009，「臺灣股票市場的反向投資策略之績效分析及因素之探討」，發表於兩岸經貿暨管理學術研討會，新竹、新豐，明新科技大學。
陳禮潭、李明煌、李存晟，2009年「技術展望與橫斷面股票報酬─臺灣實證分析」發表明2009兩岸經貿暨管理學術研討會，新竹、新豐，明新科技大學管理學院。
Lii-Tarn Chen, 2009, “Interest Rate Risk and Equity Values of Taiwan’s Banking Companies:  A GARCH-M Model,” Presented at Western Economic Association International 84 Annual Conference, June-July 2009, Vancouver, B.C., Canada.
陳禮潭，2009，「殖利率差、非貨幣政策工具變數與實質產出成長之預測—美國總體資料之實證分析」發表於第九屆全國實證經濟學論文研討會，嘉義民雄，國立中正大學。
Lii-tarn Chen, June 2008, “The Predict Power of Economic Activity Using Yield Spread: Further Evidence and a Rational Expectation Interpretation,” Presented at Western Economic Association International 83 Annual Conference, June-July 2008, Honolulu, Hawaii, U.S.A. 
陳禮潭、廖慧芳，2007，「台灣金控子銀行合併效率之分析—三階段DEA模型之應用」發表於生產力成長與效率衡量學術研討會，臺北市，中央研究院經濟研究所。
陳禮潭、陳瑞章，2007，「解析軍事投資與軍事維持之國防分項支出對台灣經濟成長的影響」發表於第十五屆國防管理學術暨實務研討會，臺北市，國防大學國防管理學院。
Lii-Tarn Chen, 2004, “Is There Any Impact of Credit Card on the Demand for Money?－A case of Taiwan,”發表於第四屆全國實證經濟學論文研討會，臺中，私立逢甲大學。
陳禮潭，2003，「資本管制與新凱因斯之菲力浦曲線－台灣之實證分析」發表於開放經濟與總體計量會議，臺北市，中央研究院經濟研究所。
Lii-tarn Chen and Cheng-Mount Cheng, 2003, “Effects of Foreign Investments on the Bargaining of a Free Trade Agreement Between Two Asymmetric Countries,” Presented at Western Economic Association International Pacific Rim Conference, Taipei, Taiwan. 
Lii-tarn Chen and Ren-Kuang Lue, 2002, Measuring Noise In The Efficiency Stock Market,”發表於第四屆全國實證經濟學論文研討會，花蓮，國立東華大學。
Lii-tarn Chen and Mei-Yuan Chen, 2001, “New Statistical Evidences on Purchasing Power Parity:  Some Empirical Results from Taiwan,” 發表於總體經濟計量模型研討會，臺北市，中央研究院經濟研究所。
陳禮潭、趙億豐，2001，「臺灣的物價是否具有完全伸縮性?」發表於第三屆全國實證經濟學論文研討會，南投，國立國際暨南大學。
Lii-tarn Chen and Pi-Chwen Hsu, 2000, “The Money Demand Function Revisited: Evidence from Financial Risk Using Taiwan Data,” Presented at the Taipei International Conference on Modeling Monetary and Financial , Taipei, Taiwan.
Lii-tarn Chen, 1999, “Imperfection of Market Structure, Financial Evolution and Economics Growth－The Case of Taiwan,” Presented at the Taipei International Conference on Economic Growth, Taipei, Taiwan.
Lii-tarn Chen and Zin-Fei Lin, Jan. 1998, “Population Growth and Technological Change：An Alternative View,” Presented at the 1998 Allied Social Sciences Association (ASSA) Conference, Chicago U.S.A., Jan. 1998.
Lii-tarn Chen and Vei-lin Chan, July 1997, “Bubbles, Model Specification Errors, and Government Budget Constraint：The Chinese Hyperinflation, 1946-1948,” Presented at Western Economic Association International 72 Annual Conference, July 1997, Seattle U.S.A.
